'''2012年奥罗拉枪击事件'''是指发生在2012年7月20日清晨，[[美国|美国]][[科罗拉多州|科罗拉多州]][[奥罗拉_(科罗拉多州)|奥罗拉市]]《[[黑暗騎士：黎明昇起|黑暗騎士：黎明昇起]]》電影首映式上的枪击事件，一名头戴[[防毒面具|防毒面具]]的枪手向奥罗拉中心（Town Center of Aurora）购物中心[[世紀電影院|世紀16電影院]]（Century 16）内正观看电影新片的观众进行扫射，并投掷了一枚催泪弹。共造成12人死亡，58人受伤。<ref name="dp120720a"/><ref name="dench120720n">{{cite news |publisher=[[The_Denver_Channel|The Denver Channel]] |title=12 Dead, 53 Hurt In Mass Shooting Inside Aurora Movie Theater |url=http://www.thedenverchannel.com/news/31289126/detail.html |date=2012-07-20 |accessdate=2012-07-20 |deadurl=yes |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20120721035733/http://www.thedenverchannel.com/news/31289126/detail.html |archivedate=2012-07-21 }}</ref> 在[[2016年奥兰多夜店枪击案|2016年奧蘭多夜店槍擊案]]前，这是美国历史上在和平时期傷亡總人數最多的枪击事件，<ref name = "ABC New Article">"[http://abcnews.go.com/US/mass-shooting-colorado-movie-theater-14-people-dead/t/story?id=16817842 Colorado Movie Theater Shooting: 71 Victims the Largest Shooting in United Staes History] {{Wayback|url=http://abcnews.go.com/US/mass-shooting-colorado-movie-theater-14-people-dead/t/story?id=16817842 |date=20190214083553 }}". ABC News. Retrieved July, 20, 2012.</ref><ref name = "Travelers Today Article">"[http://www.travelerstoday.com/articles/2391/20120720/colorado-theater-shooting-new-updates-james-holmes.htm Colorado Theater Shooting: New Updates About James Holmes] {{Wayback|url=http://www.travelerstoday.com/articles/2391/20120720/colorado-theater-shooting-new-updates-james-holmes.htm |date=20120723012527 }}". Travelers Today. Retrieved July 20, 2012.</ref><ref name = "ABC News Article 2">"[http://abcnews.go.com/politics/t/blogEntry?id=16823420 Obama Notably Silent on Gun Control After Mass Shootings] {{Wayback|url=http://abcnews.go.com/politics/t/blogEntry?id=16823420 |date=20180612162543 }}". ABC News. Retrieved July 20, 2012.</ref>本槍擊案地點距離[[科倫拜校園事件|1999年科倫拜校園槍擊事件]]案發地點只有13英里（約20.8公里）。<ref name="CNN.com_A">{{cite news |publisher=[[CNN.com|CNN.com]] |title=12 Gunman turns Batman screening into real-life "horror film" |url=http://www.cnn.com/2012/07/20/us/colorado-theater-shooting/index.html?hpt=hp_t1 |date=2012-07-20 |accessdate=2012-07-20 |archive-date=2020-12-11 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201211053430/http://www.cnn.com/2012/07/20/us/colorado-theater-shooting/index.html?hpt=hp_t1 |dead-url=no }}</ref>犯罪嫌疑人[[詹姆斯·伊根·霍尔姆斯|詹姆斯·伊根·霍尔姆斯]]随后在电影院被逮捕。

== 过程 ==
这次袭击发生在毗邻镇中心的奥罗拉商场世纪电影院第九放映厅。枪手买了票，走进电影院。据[[联邦调查局|联邦调查局]]调查，他离开了紧急出口，穿上黑色服装保护，并从停在后面出口的车上拿了武器。<ref name="cnn120720m"/>大约半个小时后他通过紧急出口返回。<ref name=custom>{{cite news|last=Muskal|first=Michael|title=Questions, but few answers, in Colorado shooting; 12 dead, dozens hurt|url=http://www.latimes.com/news/nation/nationnow/la-na-nn-colorado-shooting-update-batman-20120720,0,5201212.story|accessdate=2012-07-20|newspaper=[[Los_Angeles_Times|Los Angeles Times]]|date=2012-07-20|archive-date=2012-07-24|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20120724181738/http://www.latimes.com/news/nation/nationnow/la-na-nn-colorado-shooting-update-batman-20120720,0,5201212.story|dead-url=no}}</ref>奥罗拉警察局长Dan Oates表示：“他的所有装扮均为黑色，他身穿防弹头盔、战术防弹背心、防弹绑腿、咽喉保护和防毒面具，戴着黑色的战术手套”。<ref name="dp120720a"/><ref name="dench120720n"/><ref name="cnn120720m"/>Oates也在7月20日中午的新闻发布会上说，在电影院内枪手使用两个设备“点燃一些刺激性烟雾”分散观众。<ref>Statement by Chief Dan Oates on Channel 7 News, Denver. Date: July 20, 2012.</ref>枪手使用[[史密斯威森|史密斯威森]]的[[AR-15|AR-15]]（[[史密斯威森軍警型M&P15半自動步槍|M&P15]]）[[半自动步枪|半自动步枪]]、[[雷明登870泵動式霰彈槍|雷明登870泵動式霰彈槍]]和.40口径的[[格洛克手枪|格洛克手枪]]向电影院的人群开枪。第二把格洛克手枪在枪手停在电影院后面的白色现代车内被发现。

当枪手返回放映厅时大多数观众没有觉得什么，他穿着古怪，但其他人只认为他是为电影而打扮，只是一个恶作剧，直到他开始放烟雾，并用武器射击。<ref name=custom/>

影片中的第一开枪的场景时，蒙面枪手扔了一个冒烟的罐子，遮挡了观众的部分视线。他开始向观众开火。<ref name="hold shut"/>首先他向天花板放枪，紧接着向放映厅后面射击，之后射击通过过道的人。<ref name=running>{{cite news|last=Pilkington|first=Ed|title=Colorado theater shooting: 12 shot dead during The Dark Knight Rises screening|url=http://www.guardian.co.uk/world/2012/jul/20/colorado-theater-shooting-dark-knight?newsfeed=true|accessdate=2012-07-20|newspaper=[[The_Guardian|The Guardian]]|date=2012-07-20|archive-date=2012-08-03|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20120803204150/http://www.guardian.co.uk/world/2012/jul/20/colorado-theater-shooting-dark-knight?newsfeed=true|dead-url=no}}</ref>一些子弹穿墙打到隔壁的第八放映厅，其中正在放映同一部电影，许多人被打伤。<ref name="cnn120720m"/>一位观众看到了枪手走向出口，把门关闭并阻止他前进。<ref name="hold shut">{{cite news |title=Witness tried to keep door closed on Colo. gunman |url=http://www.google.com/hostednews/ap/article/ALeqM5hTZgLLfgDbMUjVmXVAM4ve_tj5nQ?docId=d127a37c5ecb453ba362471d86f38afb |agency=Associated Press |publisher=Google |date=2012-07-20 |accessdate=2012-07-20 |archive-date=2012-07-23 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20120723000552/http://www.google.com/hostednews/ap/article/ALeqM5hTZgLLfgDbMUjVmXVAM4ve_tj5nQ?docId=d127a37c5ecb453ba362471d86f38afb |dead-url=no }}</ref>

在0:39警方接到第一个911报警电话，警察到达现场不到90秒，立即逮捕犯罪嫌疑人。<ref name=alone1>{{cite news|last=Horwitz|first=Sari|title=Police say Colorado shooting suspect James Holmes had 2 pistols, assault rifle, shotgun|url=http://www.washingtonpost.com/world/national-security/colorado-shooter-identified-as-james-holmes-24/2012/07/20/gJQAWkdrxW_story.html|accessdate=2012-07-20|newspaper=[[The_Washington_Post|The Washington Post]]|date=2012-07-20|archive-date=2014-11-11|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20141111084100/http://www.washingtonpost.com/world/national-security/colorado-shooter-identified-as-james-holmes-24/2012/07/20/gJQAWkdrxW_story.html|dead-url=no}}</ref>袭击发生后警方询问了200多名证人，<ref>{{cite news|title=Aurora shooting: 12 dead as gunman opens fire at movie theater: live updates|url=http://www.guardian.co.uk/world/blog/2012/jul/20/denver-batman-premiere-shooting-live|accessdate=2012-07-20|newspaper=[[The_Guardian|The Guardian]]|date=2012-07-20|archive-date=2013-06-27|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20130627014823/http://www.guardian.co.uk/world/blog/2012/jul/20/denver-batman-premiere-shooting-live|dead-url=no}}</ref>调查人员认为，枪手是自己行动。<ref name=alone1/>他在袭击事件发生60天前，买了约7000发子弹。<ref>{{cite news | title = Police: Weeks of planning went into shootings that killed 12, injured scores at Batman screening in Colorado | author = M. Alex Johnson | coauthors = Pete Williams | publisher = NBC News | url = http://usnews.msnbc.msn.com/_news/2012/07/20/12850048-police-weeks-of-planning-went-into-shootings-that-killed-12-injured-scores-at-batman-screening-in-colorado | date = 2012-07-20 | accessdate = 2012-07-20 | deadurl = yes | archiveurl = https://archive.is/20130103233602/http://usnews.msnbc.msn.com/_news/2012/07/20/12850048-police-weeks-of-planning-went-into-shootings-that-killed-12-injured-scores-at-batman-screening-in-colorado | archivedate = 2013-01-03 }}</ref>在攻击中使用的枪支和弹药均为合法购买，枪是在当地的枪店买的，弹药是从网上订购。<ref name="AP Moreno">{{cite news | last = Moreno | first = Ivan | agency = Associated Press | url = http://abcnews.go.com/US/wireStory/police-colo-shooting-suspect-bought-guns-legally-16826588 | title = Police: Colo. Shooting Suspect Bought Guns Legally | publisher = ABC News | date = 2012-07-21 | accessdate = 2012-07-21 | archive-date = 2012-07-22 | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20120722041017/http://abcnews.go.com/US/wireStory/police-colo-shooting-suspect-bought-guns-legally-16826588 | dead-url = no }}</ref><ref name="auroragov updates">{{cite web | url = http://apps.auroragov.org/newsupdates/News/Updated_Media_Points_Updated_at_8.html | title = Media Updates | publisher = auroragov.org | date =  | accessdate = 2012-07-22 | deadurl = yes | archiveurl = https://archive.is/20130112131613/http://apps.auroragov.org/newsupdates/News/Updated_Media_Points_Updated_at_8.html | archivedate = 2013-01-12 }}</ref>

===枪击事件后===
警方在剧院后他的车旁逮捕了不抵抗的枪手[[詹姆斯·伊根·霍爾姆斯|霍尔姆斯]]。调查人员从车内和电影院内回收了几把枪。被捕时犯罪嫌疑人的头发是染红的，他称自己是“[[小丑_(漫画)|小丑]]”。<ref>{{cite news | url = http://abcnews.go.com/Blotter/aurora-dark-knight-suspect-joker-cops/story?id=16822251&singlePage=true | title = Aurora 'Dark Knight' Suspect James Holmes Says He 'Was the Joker': Cops | publisher = ABC News | date =  | accessdate = 2012-07-21 | archive-date = 2020-11-27 | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20201127132904/https://abcnews.go.com/Blotter/aurora-dark-knight-suspect-joker-cops/story?id=16822251&singlePage=true | dead-url = no }}</ref>霍尔姆斯被单独关押，2012年7月23日出庭。<ref>{{cite news | author = Matthew Lysiak | coauthors = James Arkin; Larry Mcshane | title = Aurora shooting suspect James Holmes jailed in solitary: 'All the inmates were talking about killing him' | url = http://www.nydailynews.com/news/national/aurora-shooting-suspect-james-holmes-jailed-solitary-inmates-talking-killing-article-1.1119173 | accessdate = 2012-07-22 | newspaper = Daily News | location = New York | date = 2012-07-21 | archive-date = 2012-07-21 | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20120721211453/http://www.nydailynews.com/news/national/aurora-shooting-suspect-james-holmes-jailed-solitary-inmates-talking-killing-article-1.1119173 | dead-url = no }}</ref>

== 受害者 ==
此次槍擊事件造成10人当场死亡，2人在医院死亡。<ref name="cnn20120720">{{cite web |url=http://www.cnn.com/2012/07/20/us/colorado-theater-shooting/index.html |title=At least 20 wounded in shooting at Colorado movie theater, official says |publisher=CNN.com |first=Chelsea J |last=Carter |date=2012-07-20 |accessdate=2012-07-20 |archive-date=2021-01-11 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210111171525/https://www.cnn.com/2012/07/20/us/colorado-theater-shooting/index.html |dead-url=no }}</ref>初步报告说，有50或53人受伤。<ref name="dp120720a"/><ref name="dench120720n"/>数字随后被更新为70人被枪击，12人死亡和58人受伤。根据[[美國廣播公司|美國廣播公司]]新闻報導指出，受害者的人数使这次事件成为美国历史上伤亡总人数最多的枪击事件（但並非死亡人數最多的事件）。<ref name="abcmass">{{cite news|url=http://abcnews.go.com/US/aurora-colo-batman-shooting-71-victims-largest-mass/story?id=16817842|last=Sandell|first=Clayton|title=Colorado Movie Theater Shooting: 71 Victims The Largest Mass Shooting|publisher=ABC News|date=2012-07-20|accessdate=2012-07-20|archive-date=2020-12-13|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201213160407/https://abcnews.go.com/US/aurora-colo-batman-shooting-71-victims-largest-mass/story?id=16817842|dead-url=no}}</ref>

伤者被送到附近的儿童医院、丹佛健康医疗中心、奥罗拉医疗中心、帕克台安医院、瑞典医院、罗斯医疗中心、大学医院，以及在袭击现场设立的一个临时医院内治疗。<ref name=Sky>{{cite web|title=Fourteen shot dead at Batman film premiere|url=http://news.sky.com/story/962756/fourteen-shot-dead-at-batman-film-premiere|work=Sky News|accessdate=2012-07-20|archive-date=2012-07-20|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20120720100643/http://news.sky.com/story/962756/fourteen-shot-dead-at-batman-film-premiere|dead-url=no}}</ref>未受伤的证人被送往附近的一所高中内。受害者的年龄介于3个月至51岁之间，最年轻的伤者是在大学医院治疗的3个月大的男孩，<ref name="Sky"/>他已出院。<ref name="abc120720e">{{cite news |first1=Clayton |last1=Sandall |first2=Kevin |last2=Dolak |publisher=[[ABC_News|ABC News]] |title=Aurora, Colorado Movie Theater Shooting: 12 Dead; James Holmes Held as Suspect |url=http://abcnews.go.com/US/mass-shooting-colorado-movie-theater-14-people-dead/story?id=16817842 |date=2012-07-20 |accessdate=2012-07-20 |archive-date=2021-01-20 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210120190330/https://abcnews.go.com/US/mass-shooting-colorado-movie-theater-14-people-dead/story?id=16817842 |dead-url=no }}</ref>公众和华纳兄弟公司已捐款近200万美元，以帮助受害者。<ref>{{cite web|last=SLEVIN and WYATT|first=COLLEEN and KRISTEN|title=No medical bills for some Colo. shooting victims|url=http://hosted.ap.org/dynamic/stories/U/US_COLORADO_SHOOTING_MEDICAL_BILLS?SITE=AP&SECTION=HOME&TEMPLATE=DEFAULT&CTIME=2012-07-25-18-56-36|publisher=AP|accessdate=2012-07-26|deadurl=yes|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20120727082043/http://hosted.ap.org/dynamic/stories/U/US_COLORADO_SHOOTING_MEDICAL_BILLS?SITE=AP&SECTION=HOME&TEMPLATE=DEFAULT&CTIME=2012-07-25-18-56-36|archivedate=2012-07-27}}</ref>

