===背景===
枪手是當時24岁的白人男子[[詹姆斯·伊根·霍爾姆斯|詹姆斯·伊根·霍爾姆斯]]（James Eagan Holmes）（生于1987年12月13日），<ref name="bbc0721" />在[[加州|加州]][[聖地牙哥_(加利福尼亞州)|聖地牙哥]]长大。<ref>{{cite news | agency = Associated Press | url = http://www.toledoblade.com/Nation/2012/07/20/Suspect-described-2.html | title = Who is James Egan Holmes? | newspaper = [[Toledo_Blade|The Blade]] | location = Toledo, OH | date = 2012-07-20 | accessdate = 2012-07-21 | archive-date = 2012-07-23 | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20120723060117/http://www.toledoblade.com/Nation/2012/07/20/Suspect-described-2.html | dead-url = no }}</ref>据邻居说，他们家在当地的[[长老教会|长老教会]]十分活跃。<ref>{{cite web |last=Burnett |first=Sara |url=http://www.mercurynews.com/nation-world/ci_21124001/colorado-shooting-suspect-james-eagan-holmes-was-honor |title=Colorado shooting suspect James Eagan Holmes was honor student |publisher=Mercurynews.com |date= |accessdate=2012-07-21 |archive-date=2012-07-22 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20120722140042/http://www.mercurynews.com/nation-world/ci_21124001/colorado-shooting-suspect-james-eagan-holmes-was-honor |dead-url=no }}</ref><ref>{{cite news |last=Stout |first=Matt |url=http://www.bostonherald.com/news/national/central/view/20220721dark_side_experts_suspects_shooting_spree_desperate/ |title=Experts: Suspect's shooting spree 'desperate' |newspaper=Boston Herald |date=2012-07-21 |accessdate=2012-07-21 |archive-date=2012-07-27 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20120727033040/http://bostonherald.com/news/national/central/view/20220721dark_side_experts_suspects_shooting_spree_desperate |dead-url=no }}</ref>他于2006年在聖地牙哥的托里高地社区Westview高中毕业，在那里他喜欢踢足球和越野跑。<ref>{{cite news | last1 = Banda | last2 = Peipert | first1 = P. Solomon | first2 = Thomas | title = Movie Massacre: Shock, Sadness, a Search for Clues | url = http://abcnews.go.com/US/wireStory/movie-massacre-shock-sadness-search-clues-16826534?singlePage=true | publisher = ABC News | agency = [[Associated_Press|Associated Press]] | accessdate = 2012-07-21 | archive-date = 2012-07-25 | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20120725100746/http://abcnews.go.com/US/wireStory/movie-massacre-shock-sadness-search-clues-16826534?singlePage=true | dead-url = no }}{{verify source|AP story was replaced | date = July 2012}}</ref><ref>{{cite news | last = Lohr | first = David | title = Colorado Shooting: What We Know About James Holmes (UPDATED) | url = http://www.huffingtonpost.com/2012/07/20/colorado-shooting-james-holmes_n_1688996.html | work = The Huffington Post | date = 2012-07-20 | accessdate = 2012-07-20 | archive-date = 2012-07-21 | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20120721130536/http://www.huffingtonpost.com/2012/07/20/colorado-shooting-james-holmes_n_1688996.html | dead-url = no }}</ref>2010年，他在[[加州大學河濱分校|加州大學河濱分校]]获得了[[神经科学|神经科学]]最高荣誉学士学位。<ref>{{cite news | url = http://www.cbsnews.com/8301-18563_162-57477097/colo-suspect-james-holmes-smart-but-quiet-teachers-and-neighbors-say/ | title = James Holmes "smart" but "quiet," teachers and neighbors say | publisher = [[CBS_News|CBS News]] | date = 2012-07-20 | accessdate = 2012-07-20 | author = Whitaker, Bill | archive-date = 2012-07-21 | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20120721072140/http://www.cbsnews.com/8301-18563_162-57477097/colo-suspect-james-holmes-smart-but-quiet-teachers-and-neighbors-say/ | dead-url = no }}</ref><ref>{{cite web |last=Burnett |first=Sara |url=http://www.denverpost.com/news/ci_21124892/theater-shooting-suspect-holmes-quiet-man |title=Theater shooting suspect: A quiet man who authorities say harbored a deadly plan |publisher=The Denver Post |date=2010-09-14 |accessdate=2012-07-21 |archive-date=2012-07-21 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20120721184839/http://www.denverpost.com/news/ci_21124892/theater-shooting-suspect-holmes-quiet-man |dead-url=no }}</ref>他还是几个荣誉协会的成员，包括Phi Beta Kappa和[[金钥匙国际荣誉协会|金钥匙国际荣誉协会]]。大學畢業後他沒找到全職工作在住家附近的麥當勞打工，他的鄰居說他看起來情緒低落很消沉。<ref>{{cite web |url=http://usnews.msnbc.msn.com/_news/2012/07/20/12854157-aurora-suspect-james-holmes-was-buying-guns-dropping-out-of-graduate-school |title=Aurora suspect James Holmes was buying guns, dropping out of graduate school |publisher=Usnews.msnbc.msn.com |date= |accessdate=2012-07-21 |deadurl=yes |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20120722200339/http://usnews.msnbc.msn.com/_news/2012/07/20/12854157-aurora-suspect-james-holmes-was-buying-guns-dropping-out-of-graduate-school |archivedate=2012-07-22 }}</ref>之後霍尔姆斯在科罗拉多州丹佛大学攻读神经科学博士学位。2012年，他的学习成绩下降<ref name="WashPostJuly20 Leonning" />，在春季综合考试表现不佳。雖然大学不打算将他开除。然而，他自己选择退学。<ref>{{cite web | url = http://www.ucdenver.edu/about/newsroom/newsreleases/Pages/Statement-from-the-university-on-James-Holmes.aspx | title = Statement from the university on James Holmes | Newsroom | University of Colorado Denver | publisher = Ucdenver.edu | date =  | accessdate = 2012-07-21 | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20120723195930/http://www.ucdenver.edu/about/newsroom/newsreleases/Pages/Statement-from-the-university-on-James-Holmes.aspx | archive-date = 2012-07-23 | dead-url = yes }}</ref>他本人先前除了一次因为超速駕駛而受罚之外，没有其他任何犯罪纪录。<ref name="cbsnews 2">{{cite news | url = http://www.cbsnews.com/8301-201_162-57476636/colo-shooting-suspect-james-holmes-apartment-booby-trapped-police-say/ | title = Colo. shooting suspect James Holmes' apartment booby trapped, police say | publisher = CBS News | date = 2012-07-20 | accessdate = 2012-07-20 | archive-date = 2012-07-21 | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20120721102834/http://www.cbsnews.com/8301-201_162-57476636/colo-shooting-suspect-james-holmes-apartment-booby-trapped-police-say/ | dead-url = no }}</ref>

===住处===
他身穿[[防弹衣|防弹衣]]，戴着[[防毒面具|防毒面具]]。<ref>{{cite web|url=http://newsfeed.time.com/2012/07/20/shooting-rampage-at-dark-knight-showing-in-colo-10-dead/|title=Shooting Rampage at Dark Knight Rises Showing in Colo.; 14 Dead|date=|accessdate=2012-07-20|archive-date=2020-11-12|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201112010844/https://newsfeed.time.com/2012/07/20/shooting-rampage-at-dark-knight-showing-in-colo-10-dead/|dead-url=no}}</ref>在影院停车场发现了他的车，车上有步枪、猎枪和手枪。犯罪嫌疑人并没有抗拒逮捕。被捕后，他告诉警察，在他居住的地方有爆炸[[诡雷|诡雷]]。<ref name="abc120720e" /><ref name="dench120720n" />警方对他住处周围进行了疏散，联邦调查局特工和警察使用梯子进入霍尔姆斯的公寓，在那里他们使用一个攝影機安装在杆子上进行调查，并证实，该公寓确实有爆炸装置。<ref name="ladder">{{cite news | title = 12 killed in shooting at Colo. movie theater | url = http://www.themonitor.com/articles/injured-62418-mall-police.html | accessdate = 2012-07-20 | newspaper = [[The_Monitor_(Texas)|The Monitor]] | date = 2012-07-20 | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20120816214757/http://www.themonitor.com/articles/injured-62418-mall-police.html | archive-date = 2012-08-16 | dead-url = yes }}</ref>警方表示“诡雷的样子看起来非常复杂。”<ref>{{cite news |agency=Reuters |url=http://www.clintonnewsrecord.com/2012/07/20/colorado-shooting-suspects-apartment-is-booby-trapped-police |title=Colo. suspect's apartment 'booby-trapped' |work=Clinton News-Record |date=2012-07-20 |accessdate=2012-07-20 |archive-date=2014-01-02 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20140102193358/http://www.clintonnewsrecord.com/2012/07/20/colorado-shooting-suspects-apartment-is-booby-trapped-police |dead-url=no }}</ref>7月21日，拆除了爆炸装置。<ref>{{cite web | url = http://www.foxnews.com/us/2012/07/20/police-work-to-id-victims-colorado-massacre-delay-probe-suspect-apartment/ | title = Authorities disarm trip wire, first explosive deivce in Colorado movie theater massacre suspect's apartment | publisher = Fox News | date =  | accessdate = 2012-07-21 | archive-date = 2015-10-31 | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20151031110418/http://www.foxnews.com/us/2012/07/20/police-work-to-id-victims-colorado-massacre-delay-probe-suspect-apartment/ | dead-url = no }}</ref>

协同调查的[[美国联邦调查局|美国联邦调查局]]说，到目前为止，没有迹象表明枪击事件同[[恐怖主义|恐怖主义]]行动有关。

===出庭受审===
2012年7月23日，头发染成橘红色的霍尔姆斯身穿红色囚服出现在科罗拉多州的法庭上，<ref name="BBC-Court1">{{cite news|url=http://www.bbc.co.uk/news/world-us-canada-18957991|title=Aurora shooting: Suspect James Holmes appears in court|date=2012-07-23|publisher=[[BBC_News_Online|BBC News Online]]|accessdate=2012-07-23|archive-date=2020-11-11|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201111215723/https://www.bbc.co.uk/news/world-us-canada-18957991|dead-url=no}}<!-- "dazed" used on webpage; "groggy" in video report --></ref>由法官发出的强制性保护令，<ref name="Ingold">{{cite news|last=Ingold|first=John|title=mercurynews.com|url=http://www.mercurynews.com/top-stories/ci_21136929|accessdate=2012-07-24|newspaper=mercurynews.com|date=2012-07-23|author2=Fender, Jessica|archive-date=2016-08-06|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160806060132/http://www.mercurynews.com/top-stories/ci_21136929|dead-url=no}}</ref>并任命了一个公共辩护人。<ref name="NYT_Healy_2012/07/24">{{cite news | date = 2012-07-23 | title = Suspect in Colorado Theater Shooting Appears in Court | author = Jack Healy | coauthor = Dan Frosch | url = http://www.nytimes.com/2012/07/24/us/suspect-in-colorado-shooting-in-court.html?pagewanted=print | work = [[The_New_York_Times|The New York Times]] | accessdate = 2012-07-23 | archive-date = 2018-06-12 | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20180612233741/https://www.nytimes.com/2012/07/24/us/suspect-in-colorado-shooting-in-court.html?pagewanted=print | dead-url = no }}</ref>霍尔姆斯什么也没说，也不看着法官，似乎一路睡意浓厚。<ref name="BBC-Court1" />
检察官正在考虑是否寻求死刑。<ref name="BBC-Court1" />

2012年7月30日，科罗拉多州检察官对霍尔姆斯提出正式指控，其中包括24项一级谋杀罪，116项谋杀未遂，藏有爆炸装置，并煽动暴力等罪名。<ref>{{cite web|title=James Eagan Holmes charged with murder, attempted murder from Colo. rampage|url=http://www.cbsnews.com/8301-201_162-57482151/james-eagan-holmes-charged-with-murder-attempted-murder-from-colo-rampage/|publisher=CBS News|accessdate=2012-07-30|archive-date=2013-11-11|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20131111213720/http://www.cbsnews.com/8301-201_162-57482151/james-eagan-holmes-charged-with-murder-attempted-murder-from-colo-rampage/|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref>{{cite web|title=James Holmes charged with 24 counts of murder in Colorado shooting|url=http://www.news-press.com/article/20120730/NATION/307300024/James-Holmes-charged-24-counts-murder-Colorado-shooting?odyssey=tab%7Ctopnews%7Ctext%7CHome|publisher=newspress.com / AP|accessdate=2012-07-30}}{{dead link|date=十一月 2017 |bot=InternetArchiveBot }}</ref>

==判決結果==
2015年8月8日陪審團裁定，2012年美國科羅拉多州戲院槍擊案的槍手荷姆斯（James Holmes）免死，但將遭判不得假釋的無期徒刑。

